OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA fine end
OL,6,Fto the day with plenty of sunshine
OL,7,Fthis evening, then staying dry and
OL,8,Fmostly clear overnight. Some low
OL,9,Fcloud, mist and fog patches are likely
OL,10,Fto form around coastal districts of
OL,11,FDevon and Cornwall. Light winds.
OL,12,
OL,13,CThursday:FEarly morning low cloud,
OL,14,Fmist and fog patches quickly clearing
OL,15,Fto leave a fine and very warm, locally
OL,16,Fhot day, with plenty of sunshine.
OL,17,FStaying cooler on coasts. Light winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
